::Kluster/Chordate::

"I'll be there," Kluster replies to Phobia, getting up to exit the ship.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Seeing the bot fly by him, Chordate activates his thrusters. "Hey, wait up!" 
he yells, flying after Riptide.
